Dear Sir /Madam

This letter is regarding the settlement offer request for the debtor mentioned above. On a without prejudice basis we are willing to accept settlement of {!Product__c.Settlement_Amount__c} on this account as long as the payment is received in our office no later than {!Product__c.Settlement_Manual_Date__c}.

Please note, if funds are not received as outlined above, this offer shall become null and void and the full balance, plus interest will become due immediately.

If you have any questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to contact us.

